{"id":4158,"date":"2019-10-03T13:00:20","date_gmt":"2019-10-03T13:00:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/?p=4158"},"modified":"2019-10-03T13:05:54","modified_gmt":"2019-10-03T13:05:54","slug":"paypal-smart-checkout","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/paypal-smart-checkout\/","title":{"rendered":"PayPal Smart Checkout"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The <strong>PayPal Smart Checkout<\/strong> is a payment gateway provided by PayPal.  The PayPal Smart Button Checkout contains a number of buttons that allow your customers to checkout using their PayPal Account, their credit card (Visa, Mastercard, etc.) or PayPal credit. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Configure PayPal Smart Checkout<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>To set up this feature you will now need to\u00a0<strong>Log in\u00a0<\/strong>to your\u00a0<strong>PayPal Developer Account\u00a0<\/strong>to locate your API details. Keep in mind that in order to use Live details, you will need a\u00a0<strong>PayPal Business Account<\/strong>. <\/li><li>Click on the\u00a0<strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/developer.paypal.com\/developer\/applications\/\" target=\"_blank\">My Apps &amp; Credentials<\/a>\u00a0<\/strong>menu within your\u00a0<strong>PayPal Developer Account<\/strong>. <\/li><li>Scroll down to the\u00a0<strong>Rest API Apps\u00a0<\/strong>section. <\/li><li>Click the\u00a0<strong>Create App\u00a0<\/strong>button. <\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"335\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-create-app-1024x335.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4159\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-create-app-1024x335.png 1024w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-create-app-300x98.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-create-app-768x251.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-create-app-60x20.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-create-app-150x49.png 150w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-create-app.png 1540w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Give your\u00a0app a\u00a0<strong>name\u00a0<\/strong>e.q. &#8220;<strong>Perfex CRM<\/strong>&#8220;<\/li><li>Click the\u00a0<strong>Create App\u00a0<\/strong>button. <\/li><li>You will now see your\u00a0<strong>Sandbox Client ID\u00a0<\/strong>and your\u00a0<strong>Sandbox Secret Key\u00a0<\/strong>(once you click the \u2018show\u2019 button). <\/li><li>Click the\u00a0<strong>Live\u00a0<\/strong>button in the left-hand corner to show your\u00a0<strong>Live API Keys<\/strong>. <\/li><li>In Perfex CRM navigate to <strong>Setup->Settings->Payment Gateways->PayPal Smart Checkout<\/strong><\/li><li>Copy and paste the needed API Credentials for your requirement LIVE or SANDBOX from your PayPal account into the settings of your Perfex CRM PayPal Smart checkout gateway.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"346\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-app-1024x346.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4160\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-app-1024x346.png 1024w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-app-300x101.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-app-768x260.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-app-60x20.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-app-150x51.png 150w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/paypal-app.png 1530w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Ensure you paste them in the correct fields. <\/li><li>Check the &#8220;<strong>Active<\/strong>&#8221; checkbox to activate the PayPal Smart Checkout gateway. <\/li><li>If you added SANDBOX API credentials, make sure to check the &#8221; Enable Test Mode&#8221; option in Perfex CRM.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"st-alert st-alert- \">If you plan to accept other currencies then your default PayPal account currency, make sure that the currencies are added into your PayPal account.<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The PayPal Smart Checkout is a payment gateway provided by PayPal. The PayPal Smart Button Checkout contains a number of buttons that allow your customers to checkout using their PayPal Account, their credit card (Visa, Mastercard, etc.) or PayPal credit. Configure PayPal Smart Checkout To set up this feature you will now need to\u00a0Log in\u00a0to [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4158","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-payment-gateways"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4158","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4158"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4158\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-